{
  "text": "We developed this score from the US data and applied it in our small population. In face of the ongoing discussion on the MELD policy in terms of justice and utility, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] there is an urgent need for further validation of all available score systems in Europe. BAR has, from our view, the greatest potential to be helpful in deciding at which point a high-risk liver transplant candidate should not be transplanted.",
